description:
The files in this repository are data required to reproduce the analysis presented in the baerhunter manuscript (A. Ozuna, D. Liberto, R. M. Joyce, K.B. Arnvig, I. Nobeli. baerhunter: An R package for the discovery and analysis of expressed non-coding regions in bacterial RNA-seq data.) . Files beginning with &quot;output&quot; in their name are the actual output of running the scripts available from https://github.com/irilenia/baerhunter_paper . 

 &nbsp; 

 A description of how to use these data is given in the R markdown scripts available from:&nbsp; https://github.com/irilenia/baerhunter_paper 

 &nbsp;

